ring semesters: Full payment of tuition and fees upon registration or by the payment deadline; or Installment payment plan: consists of an initial down payment of 10%, with 3 additional payments of 30% each. The first payment is due by the payment deadline each semester and additional payments are due by the 3rd of each month. For Fall semesters, payments will be due on October 3rd, November 3rd and December 3rd. For Spring Semesters, payments will be due on February 3rd, March 3rd and April 3rd. Payment plans are not offered for Summer sessions.* NOTE: A $20 fee is added when the installment plan is processed and is due with the initial payment. Where to find the Installment Plan option: Log in to your account at my.unt.edu with your username and password On the left side menu click "Finances" Click "Make A Payment" Click the tab for "Installment Plan" * Tuition and fees must be paid in full for each summer term upon registration or by the payment deadline. Payment for any additional fees resulting from Schedule Revision or Add/Drops is due by the end of the Add/Drop period. Tuition payment by installment is not offered during the summer sessions. Employee Pay Plan UNT provides the following options for employees for the payment of tuition and fees during the fall and spring semesters: Full payment of tuition and fees upon registration or by the payment deadline; or Installment payment plan: consists of an initial down payment of $100.00, with 3 additional payments of 33% each. The first payment is due by the payment deadline each semester and additional payments are due by the 3rd of each month. For Fall semesters, payments will be due on October 3rd, November 3rd and December 3rd. For Spring Semesters, payments will be due on February 3rd, March 3rd and April 3rd. Payment plans are not offered for Summer sessions. If an employee selects this plan, there will be no installment fees or late fees associated with this plan during the semester it was selected. Charges due for additional fees resulting from Schedule Revision or Add/Drops will be added to the installment payments. Tuition payment by installment is not offered during the summer sessions. Top Contact Us (940) 565-3225 student.accounting@unt.edu Mail Us Eagle Student Services Center Room 105 University of North Texas 1155 Union Circle #310620 Denton, TX, 76203-5017 Visit UsEagle Student Services Center Room 105 1147 Union Circle Denton, TX, 76209 [map] Main Menu Home Tuition and Fees Waivers and Exemptions Payments Refunds Short-Term Loans UNT ID Cards Tax Reporting Contact Us University Links MyUNT Blackboard EagleConnect UNT Directory UNT Map Jobs at UNT Email & Phone  Student.Accounting@unt.edu  940-565-3225 Student Accounting and University Cashiering Services   Find UNT on Google Maps   1155 Union Circle #311277 Denton, Texas 76203-5017   Visitor Information Call us Email Us UNT Map Apply now Schedule a tour Get more info Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Electronic Accessibility | Required Links | UNT Home ©2017 University of North Texas Required Links 